s/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3010d6b8f3b72d624506d0b83ffc0acc1deef538","tid":1766763,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/29XL1cvz0rc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F29XL1cvz0rc&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=cbcd8b40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/29XL1cvz0rc</a><br />\n試過也算擁有"},{"pid":"2bb618c1df7e2fbfd34e496da6e9b2ec8c43f32c","tid":1766763,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>腳趾妹幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日貼老歌</blockquote><br />\n因為本地既我只係會聽舊既  而家嗰d真係冇乜興趣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得閒既入黎我d經典po囉  薑汁兄有貼吖 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5714acd371f7d0639e6bc1f7b02de34e94e79d11","tid":1766763,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深夜港灣 😄<br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得關淑怡版本正啲</blockquote><br />\n係咩 佢嗰首唔係太熟<br />\n甄楚倩首係因為睇過黑色迷牆先識 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&